raw_text = "~ start
## 8:40am
do Story.set_location(\"dorm_kitchen\")
Mabel: BABE. Wakey wakey 🌞
Mabel: I'm up before my alarm AND I already made breakfast
Mabel: img: other/11
Mabel: Who even IS this girl 😎
Player: Whoa. Morning person Mabel is back?
Mabel: Ahem, she is
Mabel: I'm unstoppable with perfect sleep
Mabel: img: mabel/203
Player: I can tell 😄
Player: Where are you?
Mabel: Dorm kitchen silly
Mabel: Just me and my boyfriend and the morning munchies
Mabel: And some coffee!
Player: What's the plan?
if Story.has_flag(\"LOVE\"):
	Mabel: I got the Sorority thing today 🥲
	Mabel: I really hope it doesn't end too late
	Mabel: I don't want my beauty sleep gone again 😭
	Player: Yeah I feel that 😕
	Mabel: I still don't know what to expect
	Mabel: Nina says it's basically a big mingling party where all the new girls are involved
	Mabel: Supposedly we make friends and partners for life
	Mabel: Not sure what that means but I remember you said it wouldn't hurt to have more friends 😅
	Player: That's the spirit Mabes
	Mabel: Riiight?? 🥹
	Mabel: I'm doing great, super duper brave huh!
	Mabel: Thought: Okay maybe I'm still a teeny bit scared
	Mabel: But I keep telling myself, get through tonight and then it's the weekend, phew
	Mabel: I can finally relax, catch up on homework
	if Story.has_flag(\"Date4\"):
		Mabel: And then go on our date! 🥰
		Player: I'll be right here waiting
		Mabel: 🥹 you really are the best
	Mabel: Would you keep in touch with me 😇
	Mabel: Just text me, even if I'm busy... I'll see them and feel a little less lonely hehe
	Player: Sure thing!
	Mabel: PinkThought: As long as I have you by my side, I can do anything
if Story.has_flag(\"LUST\"):
	Mabel: Just class, then home, the usual I guess
	Mabel: I might be late tonight though, so might have another walk in the dark
	Mabel: Thought: I hope I don't run into...
	Mabel: Oh! Hold on a sec babe
	Mabel: sfx: none: Morning! You're up early too
	Mabel: Sorry, one of my dorm mates is using the kitchen too 😝
	Mabel: Thought: She's smilier than usual
	Mabel: sfx: none: How's your week going?
	Mabel: sfx: none: Huh? What do you mean?
	Mabel: sfx: none: S-sex? Ahaha.. yeah...!
	Mabel: Thought: W-what should I answer to that??
	Mabel: PinkThought: I mean I guess me and babe are gonna experience it together hehe
	Mabel: Thought: So I guess I'll just say..
	Mabel: sfx: none: O-Of course I have
	Mabel: She's just telling me about her day 😛😝😜
	Player: What's with the emojis? What's she saying? 😂
	Mabel: Thought: Crap!! Uh..
	Mabel: sfx: none: Ohhh. You had someone... over?
	Mabel: sfx: none: Your boyfriend you mean right?
	Mabel: sfx: none: That's sweet
	Mabel: sfx: none: H-Huh..?
	do heart(1)
	Mabel: sfx: none: ...it wasn't your boyfriend?
	Mabel: Thought: But she HAS a boyfriend. I see them eat breakfast together...
	- [...]
		Player: You've gone quiet 😅 all good?
